    "body": "This worked, but however when we log the hit it doesnt retrieve the records. \n`var preselectedCategories = ['Data', 'SQL'];\nvar search = instantsearch({\n    appId: '1VPDOL194L',\n    apiKey: 'a1c4dfaccd605139795a6ba19a46cf56',\n    indexName: 'UserActivity',\n    searchParameters: {\n        \"disjunctiveFacetsRefinements\": {\n           \"Skills.SkillName\": preselectedCategories\n        }\n    }\n});`\n\nThen adding the widget:\n`search.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.hits({\n      container: '#hits',\n      hitsPerPage: 10,\n      templates: {\n          empty: noResultsTemplate,\n          item: newTemplate\n      },             \n      transformData: function (hit) {\n          hit.stars = [];\n          for (var i = 1; i <= 5; ++i) {\n              hit.stars.push(i <= hit.rating);\n          }          \n          console.log(hit);\n          return hit;\n      }\n  })\n);`\n\nHere are the results in the console:\n![disjunctive](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/2465014/13402971/b729f500-dee0-11e5-830e-04625e49cf58.png)\n",
